se xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 05, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104are1665702797007.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/are1665702797007.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/are1665702797007.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"are1665702797007\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n More Editors\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can access editors for signatures, DTDs, global object libraries, modeled\n      properties, an language setups from the More Editors menu.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2753e1_d2754e1_d2755e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zox1665702797076.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zox1665702797076.html\" title=\"The DTD Editor allows you to load, create, or edit Document Type Definitions (DTDs) for XML data, and map them to Uniface entities and fields.\">DTD Editor</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2756e1_d2757e1_d2758e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qil1665702678751.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qil1665702678751.html\" title=\"The Signature Editor enables you to define, edit, and compile component signatures for both Uniface and non-Uniface components.\">Signature Editor</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2759e1_d2760e1_d2761e1\">Library\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2762e1_d2763e1_d2764e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hwq1665702797151.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hwq1665702797151.html\" title=\"Use this editor to define global variables that are available to all applications that use the library in which it is defined.\">Global Variable Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2765e1_d2766e1_d2767e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zxy1665702797226.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zxy1665702797226.html\" title=\"Use this editor to define messages or text strings that are available throughout the application.\">Messages Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2768e1_d2769e1_d2770e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rfl1665702797296.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rfl1665702797296.html\" title=\"Use this editor to create, edit, and delete help texts that can be displayed in a help window, to provide information about the application.\">Help Texts</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2771e1_d2772e1_d2773e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sgr1665702797426.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sgr1665702797426.html\" title=\"Use this editor to load a new glyph or view the properties and image of existing glyphs.\">Glyph Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2774e1_d2775e1_d2776e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uwa1665702797496.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uwa1665702797496.html\" title=\"Use this editor to define panels that can be used as toolbars for an application or form component.\">Panel Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2777e1_d2778e1_d2779e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wzk1665702797572.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wzk1665702797572.html\" title=\"Use this editor to define formats for drag and drop functionality.\">Formats Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2780e1_d2781e1_d2782e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"viv1665702797646.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/viv1665702797646.html\" title=\"Use this editor to define menu bars, drop-down menus, and popup menus for use in desktop applications.\">Menu Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2783e1_d2784e1_d2785e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"htd1665702797716.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/htd1665702797716.html\" title=\"Use this editor to define or modify a device translation table.\">Device Translation Table Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2786e1_d2787e1_d2788e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hir1665702797793.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hir1665702797793.html\" title=\"Use this editor to define or modify keyboard translation tables.\">Define Keyboard Translation Table Library</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2789e1_d2790e1_d2791e1\">Modeled Properties\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2792e1_d2793e1_d2794e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jcx1665702797862.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jcx1665702797862.html\" title=\"Use this editor to model a reusable value for the Database Interface property of entities. The Database Interface property defines the entity's physical characteristics in a database.\">Entity Interface Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2795e1_d2796e1_d2797e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lcl1665702797930.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lcl1665702797930.html\" title=\"Use this editor to model reusable values for the Database Interface property of fields, which defines the field's physical characteristics when stored.\">Field Interface Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2798e1_d2799e1_d2800e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tuv1665702798001.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tuv1665702798001.html\" title=\"Use this editor to model a reusable value for the Field Layout property, which controls the format of data when displayed.\">Field Layout Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2801e1_d2802e1_d2803e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"luo1665702798079.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/luo1665702798079.html\" title=\"Use this editor to model a reusable value for the Field Syntax property, which determines the format for data entered in the field.\">Field Syntax Library</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2804e1_d2805e1_d2806e1\">Language Setups\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2807e1_d2808e1_d2809e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xip1665702798149.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xip1665702798149.html\" title=\"Define the date and time properties for the selected language.\">Date-Time Properties</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2810e1_d2811e1_d2812e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sft1665702798224.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sft1665702798224.html\" title=\"Define or edit Uniface text editor messages for the current language setup.\">Editor Messages</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2813e1_d2814e1_d2815e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pnk1665702798293.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pnk1665702798293.html\" title=\"Use this editor to edit texts for the buttons which appear on panels for the current language setup.\">Button Texts</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2816e1_d2817e1_d2818e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gfd1665702798362.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gfd1665702798362.html\" title=\"Use this editor to define language-specific texts for askmess responses, and for the labels of Character Attributes that may be included in a session panel.\">Toggle Symbols</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"are1665702797007__li_d2819e1_d2820e1_d2821e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"scm1665702798431.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scm1665702798431.html\" title=\"Use this editor to define a Japanese era of the emperors, for use with Kanji.\">Japanese Era</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525842\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525842\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "More Editors Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 05, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 More Editors You can access editors for signatures, DTDs, global object libraries, modeled properties, an language setups from the More Editors menu. DTD Editor Signature Editor Library Global Variable Library Messages Library Help Texts Glyph Library Panel Library Formats Library Menu Library Device Translation Table Library Define Keyboard Translation Table Library Modeled Properties Entity Interface Library Field Interface Library Field Layout Library Field Syntax Library Language Setups Date-Time Properties Editor Messages Button Texts Toggle Symbols Japanese Era Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}